text: Gilles d'Ettore (born 23 May 1968 in Agde, Hérault) was a member of the National Assembly of France. He represented Hérault's 7th constituency from 2007 to 2012 as a member of the Union for a Popular Movement. ==References== Category:1968 births Category:Living people Category:People from Agde Category:The Republicans (France) politicians Category:Union for a Popular Movement politicians Category:The Popular Right Category:Mayors of places in Occitanie Category:Deputies of the 13th National Assembly of the French Fifth Republic Category:French people of Italian descent
